headline: Coastline Equipment Named Newest Trimble Technology Outlet
summary: Trimble® (Nasdaq: TRMB) today announced Coastline Equipment as the newest Trimble Technology Outlet. Based in Long Beach, California, Coastline will now sell Trimble grade control, site positioning systems and correction services technology directly to customers using John Deere and Hamm earthmoving equipment. This includes dozers, excavators, motor graders, soil compactors, mini-excavators and compact track loaders. Coastline will also sell Trimble technology for LevelBest/ATI and HitchDoc atta
